name: fcc-learn-http-assets
description: This is a snapshot of the code samples for the ["Learn HTTP" course](https://boot.dev/courses/learn-http) on [Boot.dev](https://boot.dev) at the time the video for FreeCodeCamp was [released on YouTube](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2JYT5f2isg4). If you want the most up-to-date version of the code, please visit the official [Boot.dev course](https://boot.dev/courses/learn-http). Otherwise, if you're looking for the files used in the video, you're in the right place!
